            "answer_text": "Simple watch \u201cBurn Notice\" No really there are some really good insights in the show. Call no one that are known acquaintances if you do use a burner phone and destroy that phone immediately. Borrow someone elses phone. The POLICE must gave a warrant to tap a phone so chances are good they wont be using voice recognition on billions of phones waiting for you to make a call but then they can tap you mothers lines waiting for you to call her. Do not provide details of your true intentions. So if you want to meet at the mall use prearranged words to indicate that. Or use cryptic words and codes that require itemd the LEO does not possess a book code is good. Remeber that the person meeting you is not skilled in shaking a tail so they might lead the LEOs to you. Best to disavow all friendships with everyone you know. But you can not just right out say what you meant or need as that give clues. Also CASH is king never use credit or debit or other electronic means to buy anything especially the burner phones that can eventually be tracked down and the imei can be flagged for tracing and tracking. In the 21st century if you use tech its hard to fly under the radar. Get ready for life looking over shoulders and trusting no one. Always be ready to move and never settling down with anyone. Once you drop your gaurd you will be picked up. Always destroy a burner phone after its use you wont be able to use it many times before its traced to you. Burner phones need to not have gps this makes tracking and pin pointing them difficult but not impossible. Also DO NOT port your number heck just get rid of it all together. That number is how they will locate you. ",
