            "answer_text": "I don't condone being a fugitive, and this information is in no way meant to assist you if from fleeing if that is in fact the case. Simply put, ditch your current cell phone at a bus station where it will be easily picked up and taken wherever and walk away, go to a pre paid phone and use it only when needed to, take out battery if you can when not in use. Best advice is this, if your a fugitive that they are looking for, then likely you committed a major crime; generally most \u201c fugitives \u201c are not sought by law enforcement they are entered into NCIC and the police wait for them to be stopped and info ran on them to catch them; if your being chased as a fugitive, turn yourself in and deal with it, better than running the rest of your life and never being able to let your guard down! ",
